${Object.entries(ticketsByCategory)
  .map(([category, count]) => `â€¢ ${category}: ${count}`)
  .join('\n') || 'â€¢ None'}

*Top Contributors:*
${topContributors || 'â€¢ None'}

*Total Tasks Completed: ${bugs.length + tickets.length}*

Great work team! ðŸŽ‰
  `.trim();
